{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":62,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_wu_fu","text":"楼主免礼，这次又有什么把戏？","tone":"疑问","chapter":227,"line_start":4,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"小人哪还敢在上将军前作奸使诈，今趟是有重要消息要向大爷面陈。","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":8,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_wu_fu","text":"坐下再说！","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"吕不韦有阴谋要害死王龁和大爷你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":14,"line_end":16},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_wu_fu","text":"他当然这么想，但办不办得到却是另一回事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":18,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"小人是在长期偷听下，一点一滴地串连起来，方能识破他们的阴谋。","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":20,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_wu_fu","text":"单美美已成为魏国王后，吕不韦还来这里干嘛？","tone":"疑问","chapter":227,"line_start":24,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"大爷有所不知，半年前我在楚国以重金买来一位国色天香的越女白雅雅，吕不韦对她颇为迷恋，故不时到醉风楼来盘桓。现在雅雅已代替美美，成为四花之首。唉！美美的离开，害得我差点没命，当然！小人绝不敢怪责项爷，小人是该受罚的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":28,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_wu_fu","text":"不要拐弯抹角，快说！","tone":"焦急","chapter":227,"line_start":34,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"首先他们是要对付王上将军，由于王上将军在赵境作战，各方面都要靠杜璧和成蟜支援，而吕不韦正是要藉杜璧之手，在李牧与王龁作战之际，抽王上将军的后腿，那后果可想而知了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":36,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_wu_fu","text":"李牧不是去了和齐人作战吗？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":227,"line_start":40,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"那只是诱王上将军深入赵境的毒计吧！","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_wu_fu","text":"你为何不早点将这么重要的事说出来，就算我不在咸阳，你也可找昌平君说呀！","tone":"焦急","chapter":227,"line_start":46,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"一来小人只听得一鳞半爪，未敢肯定。到前天杨豫告诉小人，许商在他面前夸口大爷你命不久矣，我的思绪清晰起来。许商当时说，大爷你此仗之胜，正种下你将来败亡之果。杨豫不解问他，他只说任大爷如何厉害，总斗不过李牧，便没有再说下去。于是小人想到只有害死王龁，大爷你方须与李牧在短期内一决雌雄，所以……","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":50,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":null,"text":"你去告诉昌平君，我要迟点才到。","tone":"陈述","chapter":227,"line_start":60,"line_end":60}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":[],"identity":"秦国上将军","faction":"秦国","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"穿越时空的秦国上将军","personality":{"traits":["勇武","机智","重情义","果断","正直"],"speech_style":"直率豪爽","temperament":"沉稳刚毅"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[227],"source_refs":[{"chapter":227,"line_start":1,"line_end":62,"text":"项少龙与十八铁卫来到醉风楼"}]},{"id":"char_wu_fu","name":"伍孚","alias":["楼主"],"identity":"醉风楼楼主","faction":"中立","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"醉风楼楼主，善于钻营","personality":{"traits":["圆滑","精明","胆小","善于察言观色","趋炎附势"],"speech_style":"恭敬谄媚","temperament":"谨慎多疑"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"依附求存"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[227],"source_refs":[{"chapter":227,"line_start":1,"line_end":62,"text":"伍孚亲自恭迎"}]},{"id":"char_lv_bu_wei","name":"吕不韦","alias":["相国"],"identity":"秦国相国","faction":"秦国","role":"villain","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"秦国权倾朝野的相国","personality":{"traits":["野心勃勃","老谋深算","心狠手辣","贪恋美色","善权谋"],"speech_style":"威严深沉","temperament":"阴鸷多疑"